CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, pg. 9 reads: "Homemakers See Latest in Foods, Appliances...9. Season-all displayed artisticly [sic] designed and plain storm doors and windows, plus aluminum [sic] awnings. Pat Deloquil, Moses Roberts and Jack Chimazzi demonstrated their values to the homemakers...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Pat Deloquil, Moses Roberts, and Jack Chimazzi displaying windows and other products in Season-All booth at Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
